NK041(di)017:0: rdo rje tshig bdun dang 'brel ba'i tshogs mchod dpal gyi bum bzang bzhugs so //
NK041(di)017:1: sha chang sogs ci 'byor pa'i dam rdzas bshams la /
NK041(di)017:3: +aahls chos kyi dbyings mnyam ka p+aa lar //
NK041(di)017:4: las snang srid 'dod yon tshogs su bshams //
NK041(di)017:5: h'u gis bde chen ye shes rol par gyur //
NK041(di)017:6: h+r+aihyisa rtsa gsum lha tshogs dgyes pa bskang //
NK041(di)017:8: tshogs zhing spyan 'dren zhing mchod pa 'phul ba ni /
NK041(di)017:10: o rgyan yul gyi nub byang mtshams //
NK041(di)017:12: khyed kyis rjes su bdag sgrub kyi //
NK041(di)017:14: byin gyis rlobs phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)017:15: gnas mchog 'di ru byin phob la //
NK041(di)017:16: tshogs mchod ye shes bdud rtsir bsgyur //
NK041(di)017:17: sgrub mchog bdag la dbang bzhi bskur //
NK041(di)017:18: bgegs dang log 'dren bar chad sol //
NK041(di)017:19: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK041(di)017:20: h'u bla ma rje btsun pad+ma thod phreng rtsal rig
NK041(di)017:21: 'dzin mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas pa yi rtsa gsum
NK041(di)017:22: kun 'dus rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor la mos gus gdung
NK041(di)017:23: shugs drag pos gsol ba 'debs bdag gzhan sgo gsum
NK041(di)017:24: dge tshogs longs spyod bcas snang srid 'dod yon dgyes
NK041(di)017:25: dgu ma tshang med kun bzang bde chen tshogs kyi
NK041(di)017:26: 'khor lor 'bul thugs brtses dgyes bzhes thugs dam skong
NK041(di)017:27: gyur cig gsol ba 'debs so gu ru rin po
NK041(di)017:28: che byin gyis rlobs shig rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro'i tshogs
NK041(di)017:29: mos ldan bu la mchog thun dngos grub stsol dam
NK041(di)017:30: tshig nyams chag thams cad sbyang du gsol phyi nang
NK041(di)017:31: gsang ba'i bar chad dbyings su sgrol byang chub bar
NK041(di)017:32: du 'bral med rjes 'dzin cing tshe bsod nyams rtogs
NK041(di)017:33: yar ngo'i zla bzhin 'phel bsam don lhun gyis 'grub
NK041(di)017:34: par byin gyis rlobs +aahmh'u badz+ra gu ru pad+ma sid+d+hi
NK041(di)017:35: h'u zhes pa'ang gser 'phyang lo'i dbo zla'i tshes bcu
NK041(di)017:36: la 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i yid kyi mtsho las byung
NK041(di)017:37: ba'i nor bu bsam 'phel yang dag pa mang+ga lam
